2010-09-15 Klaas Jan Wierenga   <k.j.wierenga@audioserver.nl>

	* version 1.8
	* Moved repository from private SVN repository to (private) github.com repository.
	* Generate git sha in version string.

2009-08-19 Klaas Jan Wierenga   <k.j.wierenga@audioserver.nl>

	* version 1.7
        * send SIGCONT to parent process when actual recording starts (output file opened)
          this signal can be caught in the parent process to trigger callbacks
	
2009-06-12 Klaas Jan Wierenga   <k.j.wierenga@audioserver.nl>

	* version 1.6
	* add file locking, to prevent two instances of streamget writing to the same output file
	* svn:ignore generated files
	
2008-05-29 Klaas Jan Wierenga   <k.j.wierenga@audioserver.nl>

	* version 1.5
	* improved efficiency by increasing buffer size from 8K to 64K
	  to reduce number of writes by 75%
	* improved performance by replacing fwrite by write
	* before these changes io-wait was 59% and DSK busy 98%
	* after these changes io-wait is 4% and DSK busy 6%
	
2006-03-10 Klaas Jan Wierenga   <k.j.wierenga@audioserver.nl>

	* version 1.4
	* improved logging
	
2006-07-17 Klaas Jan Wierenga   <k.j.wierenga@audioserver.nl>

	* version 1.3
	* unify log messages, add timestamp to log messages
	* prevent repeated output of same log message
	* added --version|-V option
	* fixed SEGV on closing output file when it wasn't opened in the first place
	* stricter checking on passed connect/reconnect options (should be >0)
	* enabled CURLOPT_FAILONERROR to prevent error ending up in mp3 output
	* better error message on unknown option

2006-07-13  Klaas Jan Wierenga  <k.j.wierenga@audioserver.nl>

	* version 1.2
	* open output file after first succesful read
	* use more efficient line-bufferend mode for log output (instead of unbuffered mode)


